Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.37,up,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是今天的头条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.81,up,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定要去其他社团了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.35,up,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  加入我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.73,up,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是发音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:07.23,up,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是写法相同  也不一定就代表它们发音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.57,up,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很容易出错  所以要多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.43,up,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:54.69,up,NTP,0,0,0,,冬木市新都某大楼内发生了大规模的煤气泄露事故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:51.95,up,NTP,0,0,0,,插播一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.25,up,NTP,0,0,0,,今天凌晨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:57.33,up,NTP,0,0,0,,冬木市深山町的住宅内发现了4名居民的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:03.84,up,NTP,0,0,0,,冬木市警察局称  被害者都是被尖锐的利器所刺身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:49.92,up,NTP,0,0,0,,本日社团活动中止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:55.39,up,NTP,0,0,0,,请教员和学生在18点之前离校
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:08.32,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  咱们去那家店看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:10.19,up,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  正好我也想去来着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:10.99,up,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.49,0:52:49.45,up,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎的资质很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀绫子还有间桐慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下新人赛稳胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是藤村老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得卫宫有些与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有点不好描述
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大赛前居然因为打工受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给大家添这么大麻烦你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但是有慎二和美缀你们两个人在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有我也没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同调  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本骨子  解明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成材质  解明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本骨子  变更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成材质  补强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是慎二的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也自己一个人挺到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能麻烦朋友的妹妹来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为士郎的监护人  这我可不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家务活全都由我来帮你做  所以不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我们只是偶然在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食器在上面的壁橱里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是储米箱和菜刀  然后还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先将叠肩膀中间的位置对折
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把袖子沿着折印叠起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反面也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后小心不要叠乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  其实叠成这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就从头开始再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年半前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我败给了一名年纪比我还小的顽固少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一眨眼便到了秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使肩伤痊愈我的生活也没有发生改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是因为樱目己想那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为我就是如此期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许只是件不值一提的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要说有什么发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我再也不去参加社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也想多去打打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是打算锻炼一下身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得这样也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是件微不足道的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己出门已经不再需要带钥匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吖吼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎一直在效仿切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么要当正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的你这个醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生就是学长的父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣对于士郎来说就是一位英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会想要去效仿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱你也有想去效仿的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  一成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说卫宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快来帮我招人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是慎二的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你  弓道部有没有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥也是弓道部所以应该是有兴趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘了问你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫樱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  加入我们弓道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤姐你不也是老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同调  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来又得拆开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那火红的烈焰正在逐渐湮没我当初的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是在告诫我不要一味地沉溺于回忆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这梦境的终焉  始终都会指向那一成不变的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也快从梦中醒过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱你也没必要每天都来我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兴趣只有料理和弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便将来的目标是  能做出比学长做的还好吃的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且马上就要超越学长了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天都在偷学我的独门秘方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请做好觉悟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是在学长家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理都会变得很难吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  不快点的话就赶不上晨练了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫你是在和慎二的妹妹交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有看到你们一起上学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是朋友的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是看见我们了的话倒是打个招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小僧还在修行之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还没那么大胆量去和你们搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  修好一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就要来管闲事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是好事  姑且谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我挺闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二要是有什么需要我帮忙的尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换弦调弓什么的  你很不擅长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说卫宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经和弓道部没有任何关系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是为了你自己好  我劝你还是不要再多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  今天我去食堂吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那位是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是二年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫远坂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  毕竟她是个名人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很显眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟远坂学姐不但人长得好看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长  你再也不会回弓道部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二会讨厌我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他只是不擅长和学长相处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起其他人  哥哥还是很喜欢学长的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是他不原意承认而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他其实喜欢自己讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是让人困扰的性格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么学长  我们明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我孙女承蒙你的照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是慎二的同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦家的那姑娘还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被切嗣救了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不召唤出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是会死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱  盘子拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早饭你也一点都没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晨练可以放一放的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顾问都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学后可以尽早回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道昨天晚上在深山町发生了杀人案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人抓到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来放学后的社团活动只好一时中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞  有点事情要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的话题我们一会再谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是一年级的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.18,0:22:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是没有社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有社团活动我也有很多事情要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这样的话你也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不要给美缀添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这说的什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被一个外人说教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能拜托你一点事儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓道部的一些无聊琐事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你应该干的事儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了吗  我还有其他事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你很闲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就帮帮我呗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好做你的老好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点集中过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.59,0:25:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.00,0:25:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.26,0:25:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.51,0:25:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶紧逃命才行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.51,0:25:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶紧逃命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.51,0:26:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.63,0:26:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.05,0:28:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.14,0:28:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且过于幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时又是如此失败的一次召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说登台演员已经聚齐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.07,0:28:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是演员的资质却又因为舞台的原因无法完全施展开来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.95,0:28:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.66,0:28:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离我们所追求的大仪式还相差甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.21,0:28:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.83,0:28:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦开始便无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀中之水一旦溢满
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.72,0:28:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必将有人将其饮尽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所幸  教会的监督者是那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:29:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必能够顺利处理好这场扭曲的圣杯战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.20,0:29:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯召唤出英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而英灵却又需要契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.37,0:29:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被卷入到这场仪式之中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.42,0:29:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终将会演变成一场杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.09,0:29:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说最后只需要留下一个人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.01,0:29:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召唤出的第七位Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.14,0:29:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是那个Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master是那个叫卫宫的小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.27,0:29:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是因果报应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会是不可侵犯地带  所以是不会出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.11,0:29:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  让我来看看那个男人究竟是不是歌颂福音的圣者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.35,0:30:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.27,0:30:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道为什么像你这样的三流魔术师能被选为Master
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.99,0:30:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要去见的男人会给你说明圣杯战争倒底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个很令人讨厌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.51,0:30:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在想为什么无论怎么联络你都没有回信
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.76,0:30:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果居然带来了一个奇怪的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是第七个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.65,0:31:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫言峰绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.98,0:31:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责掌管这个教会
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.78,0:31:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.41,0:31:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是Saber的Master吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实是被Saber所救
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.83,0:31:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果Master都是上流魔术师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.17,0:31:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是重新选一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.30,0:31:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重选吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.68,0:31:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你对10年前所发生的事情也没有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.56,0:31:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.15,0:31:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔术世界的万能之力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.15,0:31:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能够实现任何愿望的愿望机
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获得圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.74,0:31:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被选中的Master们互相厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.41,0:32:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其结果就是导致了一桩不幸事故的发生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.46,0:32:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其规模已经算得上是一场灾难了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.84,0:32:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.55,0:32:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.43,0:32:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在这个城市的人谁都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.39,0:32:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死伤者500人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.31,0:32:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧毁的建筑有134栋
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.52,0:32:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止都没能究明原因的那场火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.19,0:32:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是圣杯战争所引发的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.32,0:32:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.87,0:32:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.95,0:32:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许你去揭他的伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.46,0:32:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫做圣杯的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.67,0:32:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次圣杯战争中  有一个人曾一时得到过圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.43,0:32:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.06,0:33:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.14,0:33:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯并没能得到完成
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开战争的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.69,0:33:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没法得到圣杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.19,0:33:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的好像你亲眼所见一样
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.66,0:33:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是亲眼所见
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾被选为Master
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参与了上一次的圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.71,0:33:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.34,0:33:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是中途参战的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.96,0:33:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我做出了错误的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.22,0:33:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果  我只得到了空的圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.47,0:33:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.56,0:33:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然话才说到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.65,0:33:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了个性急的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.53,0:33:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你知道爱因兹贝伦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.29,0:34:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么少年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.12,0:34:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.21,0:34:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来下决心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.21,0:34:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.13,0:34:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说10年前那场灾害的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.80,0:34:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是圣杯战争所引起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.14,0:34:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一名Master去参战
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.69,0:34:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愉悦吧少年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.24,0:34:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望终将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.08,0:34:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要做正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.87,0:34:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要去打倒邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.09,0:34:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant是不可能记得的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.39,0:35:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话讲完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.10,0:35:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.61,0:35:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.40,0:35:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅斯菲尔・冯・爱因兹贝伦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我关门
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.83,0:35:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就要开杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.58,0:35:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.86,0:36:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.79,0:36:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.96,0:36:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.84,0:36:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键时刻Archer居然不在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.76,0:36:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙能再生  先把头颅砍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.54,0:36:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.54,0:36:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.00,0:37:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直是无聊到了极点
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.71,0:37:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.71,0:37:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.23,0:38:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿时的我一直憧憬成为正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.24,0:38:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄是有时间限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.82,0:38:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大成人之后就很难自称英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.04,0:38:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.37,0:38:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为谁的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.71,0:38:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味着要成为谁的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.14,0:38:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.81,0:38:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能成为正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.32,0:38:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.78,0:38:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.36,0:38:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.83,0:38:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.96,0:39:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.21,0:39:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是远坂为我治疗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.42,0:39:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.59,0:39:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那伤口是Master你自己治愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.55,0:39:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.64,0:39:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就可能是和Saber的契约有关
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.19,0:39:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.90,0:39:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来给我解释一下你刚刚的举动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没做什么错事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.69,0:39:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本可以做得更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.57,0:39:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Servant是要依赖Master的魔力供给的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没了魔力供给  我们就没法存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.42,0:39:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.88,0:39:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.00,0:39:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该去治疗我自己的Servant了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.35,0:39:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  下次再见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.51,0:39:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.15,0:40:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber的伤没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.57,0:40:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事  虽然还没有恢复完全
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.21,0:40:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  Saber你也想要得到圣杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.01,0:40:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是为了圣杯才出现在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.39,0:40:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得Berserker的Master  是叫爱因兹贝伦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的孩子都参加了圣杯战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.86,0:40:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在使用魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不是Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.45,0:41:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.70,0:41:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master  请指示
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.59,0:41:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.85,0:41:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.35,0:41:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在这里设置了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.77,0:41:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.61,0:41:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.42,0:41:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.52,0:42:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.53,0:42:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让我大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.49,0:42:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是卫宫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.41,0:42:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.54,0:42:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想让弓道部部长帮个忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.09,0:42:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的Servant吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.06,0:42:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来介绍一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.10,0:42:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是我的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.02,0:42:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说卫宫  让她们俩打一架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.07,0:42:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想看一场Servant之间的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.45,0:43:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.82,0:43:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会成为Master
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.74,0:43:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家可是拥有悠久历史的魔术世家
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.50,0:43:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被世人称作是圣杯战争的三大家族
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.88,0:43:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是不想让你这种门外汉知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.01,0:43:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为间桐家长子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.64,0:43:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加圣杯战争不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.85,0:43:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.14,0:43:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是一如既往的不解风情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.86,0:43:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.36,0:43:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场游戏可是相当真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.29,0:43:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.48,0:44:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.24,0:44:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁允许你在这躺着了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.60,0:44:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.61,0:44:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.40,0:45:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快给我站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.90,0:45:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样岂不是显得我要更弱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.87,0:45:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.58,0:45:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.50,0:45:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.71,0:45:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.18,0:45:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.26,0:45:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二  看来这对你的负担还是太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.32,0:45:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来间桐家就得就此退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.74,0:45:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾至极
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.37,0:45:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.95,0:45:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷等一下  我才是间桐家的魔术师啊  我才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:46:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然废物就是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.55,0:46:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家的血统己经衰败了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.13,0:46:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你没有任何的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.14,0:46:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.98,0:46:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.73,0:46:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.69,0:46:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说樱也被迫成为Master了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.52,0:46:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要提到那家伙的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.90,0:46:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.24,0:46:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那种垃圾  怎么可能会懂魔术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家的魔术真传是只属于我一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.14,0:46:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.85,0:47:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是圣杯战争的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.56,0:47:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么应该交给监督者才对
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.08,0:47:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  才过了几个小时就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.43,0:47:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.05,0:47:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是被什么不干净的东西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.27,0:47:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.11,0:47:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时由我来照看她
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.67,0:48:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.42,0:48:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀她怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.29,0:48:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该做的我都己经做了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.55,0:48:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.17,0:48:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过比起她
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.88,0:48:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎你的伤要更重一些
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.18,0:48:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.06,0:48:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10年前的那场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.56,0:48:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的面前有个男人受了和你一样重的致命伤但仍然屹立不倒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.53,0:48:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人是我最后的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.87,0:48:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并在上一次圣杯战争中取得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.20,0:48:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.08,0:48:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.42,0:48:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.68,0:48:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美缀已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:48:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.18,0:49:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是花了不少时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.81,0:49:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.73,0:49:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问了他一些关于我父亲的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.11,0:49:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.08,0:49:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.91,0:49:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫卫宫切嗣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.67,0:49:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用一句话来概括的话就是个杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.96,0:49:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以暗杀魔术师为职的魔术师杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.63,0:49:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说魔术师都是一群脱离道德的人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.39,0:49:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个男人要更加的恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.52,0:49:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在上一次圣杯战争中也被召唤到这个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.23,0:49:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为爱因兹贝伦家的Servant而战
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.86,0:49:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时的Master就叫做卫宫切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.36,0:49:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.49,0:49:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他简直就是个冷酷到极点的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.37,0:50:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了胜利会不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.33,0:50:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要对方是Master即使向他再三求饶也都被赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.13,0:50:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些Master之中  切嗣把那位神父视为最强的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.46,0:50:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说  在他和我之间
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有互相杀戮这一个选择
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.18,0:50:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和切嗣一起参加了圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.77,0:50:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并取得了最终的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.06,0:50:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.57,0:50:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫切嗣在最后的最后背叛了圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.36,0:50:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯被他破坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.29,0:50:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会为了拯救十个人而牺牲一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.67,0:50:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个无可救药的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.28,0:51:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.45,0:51:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.57,0:51:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会放着那些在圣杯战争中受害的人不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.70,0:51:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直梦想着能成为他那样的正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.17,0:51:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.63,0:51:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在说有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.84,0:51:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber我希望你能和我一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.85,0:51:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论我经历过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.47,0:51:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master手上的令咒都将我们紧紧地连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.65,0:51:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  就请叫我士郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.65,0:52:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就称你为士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.28,0:52:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我果然还是更喜欢这个读音
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.13,0:52:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.34,0:52:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.34,0:52:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  原来是切嗣先生的熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.47,0:52:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过行李没有送到还真是糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.81,0:52:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直是抱歉让你穿士郎的旧衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.15,0:52:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.11,0:52:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.52,0:52:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣先生还真是个罪孽深重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.57,0:52:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我知道他经常出国
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.49,0:52:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我很想听听你和切嗣先生之间的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.00,0:52:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.41,0:52:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然叫你过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.04,0:52:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.58,0:52:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.59,0:52:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上你有见到慎二吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.13,0:53:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到了  请问出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.51,0:53:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要是没事的话就好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.23,0:53:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.48,0:53:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.15,0:53:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.61,0:53:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.78,0:53:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二打的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.30,0:53:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.18,0:53:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连Servant都不带在身边就直接来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.22,0:53:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胆子还真是大
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.39,0:53:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你是在小看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.90,0:54:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了远坂  我有事要和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.12,0:54:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.45,0:54:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二成了Master  绫子被卷了迸去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.45,0:54:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后Rider消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.25,0:54:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  总不能就只有这些事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.22,0:54:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二他有一个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.06,0:54:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫做樱
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.27,0:54:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.65,0:54:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱有可能会被卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.70,0:54:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二那家伙似乎并没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.74,0:54:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.54,0:54:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我觉得让她住在你家保护起来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.71,0:55:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她对你来说很重要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.32,0:55:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.07,0:55:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的早餐真的是大好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.74,0:55:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还为我准备午餐  真的要好好感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.16,0:55:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这没什么  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.67,0:55:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有什么我能帮上忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.64,0:55:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.14,0:55:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那就
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.94,0:56:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.69,0:56:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这些都用得上就全买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.78,0:56:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.45,0:56:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的行李送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.16,0:56:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.70,0:56:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是欠了远坂好几个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.25,0:56:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.96,0:56:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们确实需要目用品
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.42,0:56:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是未免买得有些太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.47,0:56:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了  藤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.30,0:56:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算从今天开始让樱先住在我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.85,0:56:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  你这是抽的哪门子疯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近外面不是很危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.07,0:56:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且慎二最近挺忙的也不怎么回家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.07,0:56:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.95,0:56:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.83,0:57:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.67,0:57:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去整理一下Saber小姐的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.47,0:57:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也过去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.85,0:57:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是不想让樱误会你让Saber住在这里的事情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.27,0:57:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想什么呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说小樱她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.74,0:57:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当有料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.53,0:57:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.62,0:57:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.54,0:57:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱她
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.01,0:57:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.55,0:57:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.56,0:58:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是马上就派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.86,0:58:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再多呆一会
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.82,0:58:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会再陪你30分神的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.32,0:58:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.74,0:58:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.08,0:58:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你照顾我了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.88,0:58:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.42,0:58:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.84,0:58:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于刚刚的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.72,0:58:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.89,0:58:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要让我住在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.06,0:58:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.44,0:58:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.07,0:58:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.73,0:58:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只要你在这里我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.20,0:59:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.58,0:59:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.35,0:59:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟是魑魅魍魉一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.47,1:00:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗一郎  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.31,1:00:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起呆这里
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.90,1:00:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Assassin  快点出来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.03,1:00:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.51,1:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗一郎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.93,1:00:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.48,1:00:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人  是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.82,1:01:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先砍了他的头
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.78,1:01:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断其手脚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.99,1:01:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后将他开膛破肚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.95,1:01:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他仍然在动
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.00,1:01:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真正的Assassin吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.59,1:01:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女  赶快将我解放出来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.12,1:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你满意了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.81,1:02:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.27,1:02:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.27,1:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫你想做什么都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.71,1:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.60,1:03:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  学长
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.61,1:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.11,1:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继前几天发生的那起原因不明的煤气泄漏事故
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.99,1:03:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在冬木市新都再次发生了煤气泄露事故
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.84,1:04:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.64,1:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.18,1:04:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是藤姐啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.14,1:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来不了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.09,1:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚去了柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.93,1:04:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于新都的昏睡事件
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.01,1:04:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力反应均流向了柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.72,1:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer也恢复了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.47,1:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去调查了一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.94,1:05:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说结论
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.77,1:05:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caster把柳洞寺当作了自己的据点
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.07,1:05:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.45,1:05:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到达那里的时候  Caster已经不知被谁给杀害了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.08,1:05:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺院的人都因为被夺走了魔力而昏睡不起
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.00,1:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后唯一惨遭杀害的葛木老师
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.13,1:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕就是Caster的Master
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.14,1:05:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后接下来才是正题
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.18,1:05:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上新都再次发生了昏睡事件
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.85,1:05:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明Caster都已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.99,1:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱其实是在你家呢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.79,1:06:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.95,1:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天开始住在我家的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.67,1:06:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说卫宫同学  我们要不要合作
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.01,1:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这次和父亲说的有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.51,1:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我想先弄清是到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.77,1:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间限制的合作作战吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.02,1:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.99,1:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.16,1:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为和毫无能力的Master合作是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.12,1:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.54,1:06:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说错了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.00,1:06:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.04,1:06:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要服从Master的命令哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.05,1:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些突然  今天晚上能出来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.93,1:07:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和Archer的Master合作吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.64,1:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.65,1:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些唐突实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.86,1:07:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.23,1:07:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果能快点结束圣杯战争的话
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.78,1:07:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱估计也能回到原来的生活中去
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.82,1:07:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.87,1:07:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱果然是身体情况不太好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.12,1:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.12,1:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我多虑了的话还好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.76,1:07:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.93,1:07:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.48,1:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么  卫宫
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.49,1:07:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是樱的亲哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.78,1:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我可爱的妹妹带回家有什么不对的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.58,1:08:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有打妹妹的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.71,1:08:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙连累了美缀
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.84,1:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绝对不会把樱交给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.84,1:08:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.92,1:08:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才刚对樱出手没几天
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.51,1:08:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为欲求不满不想放手吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.72,1:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.39,1:08:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.73,1:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.28,1:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这副表倩
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.49,1:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们动手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.61,1:08:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次那场战斗还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.16,1:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.70,1:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.71,1:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么我都会听的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.46,1:08:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可请你不要在学长面前动手
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.89,1:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.39,1:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可千万不要忘记你刚刚说过的话
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.52,1:09:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.78,1:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.28,1:09:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱你不需要道嗽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.07,1:10:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  根本没法集中
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.62,1:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.25,1:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是樱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.84,1:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.05,1:10:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能稍微和学长说说话吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.97,1:10:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.53,1:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.11,1:10:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的事  我替哥哥向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.95,1:10:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不必在意的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.29,1:11:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.92,1:11:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.93,1:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.27,1:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.27,1:11:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你把它修好了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.11,1:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.61,1:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是花了我好长时间
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.99,1:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.54,1:11:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.50,1:11:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.37,1:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前的事清了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.00,1:11:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我还不认识学长你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.59,1:11:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个晚霞一片通红的傍晚
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.85,1:11:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校园和走廊都被映得一片通红
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.56,1:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很漂亮  但却十分空寂
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.06,1:12:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那时  校园里有一个人在练习跳高
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.03,1:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我还不是一个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.62,1:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一边注视着那个人  一边心里想着让那个人失败
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.92,1:12:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.23,1:12:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人无论跳多少次最后都没能成功
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.44,1:12:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后认为自己跳不过去便收拾好之后一个人回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.86,1:12:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.66,1:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.45,1:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.58,1:13:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是现在在我身边的学长你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.29,1:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从那时起我就已经知道学长了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.80,1:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.42,1:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我倒是头一次听说
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.64,1:13:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  学长
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.81,1:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知这话该不该说
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.48,1:13:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听藤村老师说
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.78,1:13:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你是被收养的养子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.28,1:13:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.16,1:13:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你不会在意这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.91,1:13:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然花了好久才适应过采
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.63,1:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也没什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.46,1:13:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长身边的人一定都很温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.09,1:14:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我周围的大人都靠不住
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.35,1:14:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣他相本就不会做家务
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.73,1:14:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤姐又是那样一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.27,1:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就这样开始自己做家务了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.69,1:14:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想变成像切嗣那样的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.99,1:14:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想成为正义的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.42,1:14:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.59,1:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.51,1:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.43,1:14:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有个问题想问
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.44,1:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我变成了一个坏人的话
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.61,1:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长你会原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.99,1:15:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果樱做了坏事的话我一定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.08,1:15:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会第一个来教训你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.54,1:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.29,1:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是学长的话就好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.97,1:15:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.22,1:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长  晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.37,1:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深山本部呼叫深山各急救车辆
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.87,1:15:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深山本部呼叫深山各急救车辆
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.46,1:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中心发来通知
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.00,1:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新都车站前大楼内有多人需要救助
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.13,1:15:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请附近的车辆尽快赶往现场进行救助
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.84,1:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深山急救呼叫…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.70,1:16:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.78,1:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.34,1:16:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  像你这种肮脏的沙虫
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.76,1:16:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没有那个能力的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.92,1:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是跑不掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.26,1:17:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾奇者
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.39,1:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.97,1:20:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.01,1:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是与生俱来的  投掷武器对我是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.35,1:20:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是流矢加护吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.61,1:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将涂黑的武器藏匿于黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.69,1:20:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊至极
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.35,1:21:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到我的脸了吗  Lancer
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.35,1:21:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我接下来要做的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.74,1:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.70,1:21:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区沙虫来跑到水里来看你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.25,1:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是还不动手的话可是会被吞噬掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.79,1:22:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.25,1:22:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.55,1:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.86,1:22:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝具
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.62,1:22:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妄想心音
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.51,1:22:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝具
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.76,1:22:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  在这里做个了断
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.14,1:23:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿刺死棘之枪
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.70,1:23:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.18,1:24:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是槽糕透了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.42,1:25:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.27,1:25:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.90,1:25:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们边走边说
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.32,1:25:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经被人监视了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.41,1:25:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是你干的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.29,1:25:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐家的老爷子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.26,1:25:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是远坂家的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.10,1:25:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是优秀
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.31,1:25:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏砚
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.27,1:25:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐不是已经退出了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.57,1:26:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老朽我可没承认我输了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.33,1:26:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.84,1:26:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.93,1:26:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然玩弄英灵的尸体
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.28,1:26:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber小心  那把剑是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.83,1:26:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰那把剑
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.84,1:27:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑是魔术破戒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.43,1:27:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会切断与Master的契约吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.97,1:27:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.06,1:27:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本打算速战速决的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.92,1:27:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  她的魔术对Saber不起作用
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.34,1:27:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果连同Master一起干掉的话会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.64,1:28:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.23,1:28:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.77,1:28:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.53,1:28:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.82,1:28:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.28,1:28:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个究竟
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.86,1:28:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.56,1:28:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚数空间
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.86,1:28:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.99,1:28:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  这不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.77,1:29:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caster  消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.61,1:29:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.66,1:29:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.24,1:29:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.04,1:29:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有直接接触到本体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.33,1:29:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶多就是和被传染了疟疾一个程度
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.29,1:29:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.63,1:29:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道刚刚那个是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.59,1:29:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.09,1:30:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚刚吸光人们魔力的就是那个黑影吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.64,1:30:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.69,1:30:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.69,1:30:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.40,1:30:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.44,1:30:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来暂时不能优先了结私人恩怨了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.34,1:30:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.43,1:30:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.72,1:30:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有我在还是让士郎受了伤
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.47,1:30:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.18,1:30:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然学长只会继续痛苦下去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.92,1:31:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.59,1:31:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地叫你出来真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.18,1:31:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我提前到了所以就先点了些东西吃
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.39,1:31:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.73,1:31:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.32,1:31:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有心情吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.57,1:31:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要和我说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.92,1:31:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎  昨天晚上你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.97,1:32:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我正以我自己的方式来监督着这次圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.81,1:32:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛已经和我说了关于柳洞寺的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.19,1:32:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同间桐脏砚交手了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.23,1:32:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他带着Caster
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.95,1:32:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像是在操纵她的尸体
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.74,1:32:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位老爷子也终于出手了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.08,1:32:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.42,1:32:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你一件连凛都不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.13,1:32:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caster在柳洞寺被杀的那天夜晚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.09,1:32:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个Servant冲破结界逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.10,1:32:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.06,1:32:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.97,1:32:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.35,1:32:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.65,1:33:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的Lancer看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.45,1:33:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过我也是一名Master
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.41,1:33:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.83,1:33:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.83,1:33:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不清头绪
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.29,1:33:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令Lancer去监视Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.26,1:33:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追到柳洞寺之后就再也没回来
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.30,1:33:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被Assassin干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.56,1:33:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Assassin很擅长隐蔽自己的气息
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.35,1:33:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而自身的战斗力却并不高
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.15,1:33:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常交手的话Lancer应该是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.78,1:33:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.62,1:33:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨晚看到的大概不只有间桐脏砚和Caster吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.39,1:34:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐泊是Assassin知道这一点故意把Lancer引过去的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.19,1:34:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在那的东西不仅仅只对Servant下手
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.81,1:34:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连街上的无辜民众也不放过
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.44,1:34:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把Caster吸取人类魔力的行为比作抽血的话
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.99,1:34:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那东西就相当于进食一样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.00,1:34:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是继续这么袖手旁观下去
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.59,1:34:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市的人就全都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.47,1:34:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去意识的人居然有30人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.40,1:35:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点在深山南四丁目
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.02,1:35:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里究竟有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.11,1:35:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.00,1:35:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.25,1:35:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.17,1:35:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是死也不会和你一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.60,1:35:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.50,1:35:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.00,1:36:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  樱是住在你家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.34,1:36:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.47,1:36:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.47,1:36:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.39,1:36:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就应该不会和一无所知的她突然相遇了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.64,1:36:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备跟踪脏砚
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.23,1:36:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去间桐家
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.69,1:36:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.69,1:36:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和间桐家有段孽缘
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.11,1:36:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老一代魔术师之间的斗争就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.20,1:36:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说卫宫同学
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.46,1:36:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.34,1:36:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.30,1:36:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道学长和你到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.59,1:36:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道即便是我问了你也不会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.22,1:36:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.39,1:37:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是学长昨晚受了伤
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.98,1:37:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望学长他遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.49,1:37:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去追踪那个黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.78,1:37:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放着它不管
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.20,1:37:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有无辜的人被卷了进来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.12,1:37:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.21,1:37:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就继续合作
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.09,1:37:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.92,1:37:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会放过那个黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.97,1:37:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.97,1:37:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.89,1:37:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到搞清楚那到底是什么东西为止
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.60,1:37:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.46,1:38:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被樱埋怨了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.96,1:38:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说昨天夜里没能保护好士郎是因为我的能力还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.18,1:38:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是我自己倒下的而已
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.85,1:38:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说根本原因  还是因为我没能阻止士郎你去参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.15,1:38:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.11,1:38:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会和你并肩作战  保护好你的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.07,1:38:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.37,1:38:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是为了樱
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.10,1:39:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.19,1:39:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.40,1:39:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.61,1:39:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  那是Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.40,1:39:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呆在那别动
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.24,1:39:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.33,1:39:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓飞蛾扑火  说的就是你这种
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.38,1:39:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间桐  脏砚
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.86,1:39:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股风压
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.03,1:39:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被迎面击中可不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.32,1:40:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风啊  肆虐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.42,1:40:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避风之加护
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.68,1:40:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对常行于沙漠的人来说可是必备的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.35,1:40:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不攻过来也无妨
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.94,1:40:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可别忘了  我的御主可正在盛情款待你的御主呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.98,1:40:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.65,1:40:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要吸引你的注意就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.09,1:41:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.34,1:41:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.26,1:41:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Servant是无法抵抗那个黑影的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.35,1:41:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是如此纯粹的你  只要被它碰到也会失去理性
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.06,1:41:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.36,1:41:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心脏  就由我来收下了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.87,1:41:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同调  开始
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.75,1:41:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭一根木棒能干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.68,1:41:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妄想心音
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.12,1:42:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.82,1:42:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是最强的Servant
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.49,1:42:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其被夺去心脏
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.95,1:42:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却选择了同自身的黑暗斗争吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.30,1:43:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.10,1:43:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身为Master应该是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.43,1:43:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的Servant已经从这个世上消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.57,1:43:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.19,1:44:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就交给你了  Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.06,1:46:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你没什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.86,1:46:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.19,1:46:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.61,1:46:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.69,1:47:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是个什么东西
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.21,1:47:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.30,1:47:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我已经
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.76,1:48:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是一名Master了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.83,1:48:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.58,1:48:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里居然是修炼场
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.04,1:48:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然  居然会有这种地方
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.88,1:49:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该是会轻蔑我的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.30,1:49:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用他人的生命来延续日趋腐朽的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.48,1:49:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.31,1:49:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您对生命的执念  正是吾主所应具备的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.37,1:49:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有鹰呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.49,1:49:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说鹰吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.50,1:49:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞拉  去给我准备一下车
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.46,1:50:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始我也要去城里
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.22,1:50:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是哪位
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.97,1:50:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她是爱因兹贝伦的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.57,1:50:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我输了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.17,1:50:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.55,1:50:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.51,1:50:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.35,1:50:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是圣杯啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.77,1:50:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为了得到圣杯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.60,1:50:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了住手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.44,1:51:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁  为什么要阻挠我
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.41,1:51:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我是谁
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.67,1:51:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种问题  你一看不就知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.81,1:52:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.27,1:52:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是去哪了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.36,1:52:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又弄的满身是伤
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.41,1:52:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你多珍惜一下自己的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.42,1:52:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.04,1:52:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.76,1:52:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.67,1:52:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.88,1:52:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.06,1:52:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.39,1:53:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.39,1:53:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.50,1:53:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  切嗣
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.96,1:53:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.42,1:53:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底应该怎样做
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.01,1:53:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能成为正义的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.32,1:59:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不能就此结束
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.41,1:59:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所应面对的敌人是
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.91,1:59:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长  我
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.00,1:59:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只要呆在这里  就能遇到那位大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.34,1:59:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂家佣有魔术资质的孩子有两个
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.22,1:59:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从最重要的人那里得到最重要的东西  这已经是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.02,1:59:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在赶快去死一下吧  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.53,2:00:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
